 16375, "last_played": 1582997709}, "language": "english", "review": "X3 is one of those games where you need to spend about 20 hours or more just learning how everything works.  Controls are kinda all over the place, stuff can be pretty janky at times, and overall it's just a pretty old game which can give it that outdated feeling.\n\nBUT... I have yet to find another game that lets me live out my fantasy of establishing a space weed/arms dealing empire across the galaxy in this much detail.\n\nGreat game, but there is definitely a very steep learning curve which will deter a lot of people.", "timestamp_created": 1736975488, "timestamp_updated": 1736975488, "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "weighted_vote_score": 0, "comment_count": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "received_for_free": false, "written_during_early_access": false, "primarily_steam_deck": false}, "185667312": {"recommendationid": "185667312", "author": {"steamid": "76561198361399164", "num_games_owned": 0, "num_reviews": 3, "playtime_forever": 32925, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 4, "playtime_at_review": 32921, "last_played": 1736971931}, "language": "russian", "review": "\u043a\u043b\u0430\u0441\u0441", "timestamp_created": 1736971701, "timestamp_updated": 1736971701, "voted_up": true, "votes_up": 0, "votes_funny": 0, "weighted_vote_score": 0, "comment_count": 0, "steam_purchase": true, "received_for_free": false, "written_during_early_access": false, "primarily_steam_deck": false}, "185127943": {"recommendationid": "185127943", "author": {"steamid": "76561197964238519", "num_games_owned": 0, "num_reviews": 427, "playtime_forever": 10964, "playtime_last_two_weeks": 0, "playtime_at_review": 10964, "last_played": 86400}, "language": "english", "review": "The X franchise (which I was introduced to with X2: The Threat) has produced the best singleplayer 3D space sandbox simulators I've ever played.\n\nX3: Terran Conflict is no exception.  There's just something that hits different about being ab